            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/Grounding_Vetiver_485ab661-3c8e-4c2a-985d-1d03d3fecee8.png",
            "content": "A smoky blend of sweet orange, coriander seed and vetiver, inspired by a spice bazaar.",
            "blend": "<div>\n    <h4 class=\"font-lausanne\">Top notes</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n<span class=\"fw-400\">Sweet Orange</span><br>Uplifting, with a sweet-citrus aroma</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n    <h4 class=\"font-lausanne\">Middle notes</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n<span class=\"fw-400\">Coriander</span><br>\nA spicy, warm scent</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n    <h4 class=\"font-lausanne\">Base notes</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"font-lausanne fw-200\">\n<span class=\"fw-400\">Vetiver</span><br>A calming oil with an earthy, grassy scent</li>\n    </ul>\n</div>"
